https://www.reddit.com/r/tableau/comments/1k0865x/tableau_to_power_bi_migration/
1. There is no tool in the market that can migrate Tableau to Power BI directly.
2. The feature sets and the entire modeling/programming paradigm are different.
3. If Microsoft has not developed this tool, the chance of us or other team doing so is slim to none. If they could, they would be selling a product worth millions.
4. Backend file type of each: it is run by connection to other databases.


